title: Hour 3 - Russell Wilson, Plaxico Burress

description:
In hour 3, Colin lets it be known that the Seahawks are not a better team without him. And situationally the Denver OC is not making the right calls. Plaxico Burress joins to talk Kenny Pickett, NFL and more.
